data.description: Eligible for VA Assumption $575k at 2.65%.This 3 bd 2.5 bth turnkey rambler nestled on a lrg corner lot is everything you have dreamed of! 1910 sq ft of 1 level living, private setting, & fully fenced backyard w/ inground pool, RV/ Boat parking behind gate, NO HOA! Fully renovated from top to bottom within last 3 years including, roof, windows, siding, furnace, water heater, interior & exterior paint, fixtures, appliances, plumbing, electrical. This open concept kitchen has newer Samsung appliances +wine fridge. The perfect home for entertaining guests w/great rm that leads out back to oversized patio & pool. In 2020 pool was re-plastered & had all new equipment installed. Easy I-5 JBLM access & mins to Tac. Golf & Country Club. 3D Tour!
